        "TileImage": "$($repository 36eab2c5-79b3-4aca-bf8b-8b40ff64c3d5).Image",
        "Description": "47, we have a problem.\r\rOur client has reported that singer-songwriter Cristina Dionisi may have beef with the Japanese singer Ado, and was caught red-handed attempting to sabotage the Italian venue for the latter&apos;s Hibana World Tour last year.\r\rCristina spent a few months in jail for attempted murder, but has clearly not learned her lesson because Marco Abiatti bailed her out. You have 90 seconds to make her learn that lesson.\r\rAdomination is inevitable.\rGood luck, 47.",
